captions.text:
- My favorite fast food fries
are hands down McDonalds.

- McDonalds or In-n-Out
are like the top two.

- It's good but it's
not like mind blowing.
- A flavor reminiscent of a fried Q-Tip.

- There's no salt on it
so there's no seasoning.
- There are certain fries that can

stand alone without ketchup,
these are not those fries.

- Taking a bite of one
is like taking a bite

of my entire childhood
and the America flag.

- It's like a french fry that
you would make out of Playdoh.
- It's had a little cosmetic surgery.

- They just taste exactly
what a fry should taste like.

- This are good, these are
like gourmet fast food fries.
It's like this is fresh from the farm.
- Ew, ew, ew, ew, ew, ew.
- There's a flavor here that I'm detecting

that's unlike any other
fry flavor I've ever had.
- I don't even know what it is.
- I'm finishing it, it's so gross.
- These taste like bowling alley fries.
- has a weird, there's another flavor.
- This is very good but it has a taste.
- Yeah this is winning for sure.
- That's a very long french fry.
- I've had these fries, I don't know
- These taste like fries made by a place

- Alright, I'm going to go
with Carl's Jr. on this one
I think they like, revamped their fries.
- It's got a little bit of crunch.
A little bit of sogginess to it.

- Crunchy on the outside,
smooth on the inside.
- Are you saving these for anyone else,
or can I just eat them all?

- I mean this is a great
day like I just came to work
and now I'm eating french fries.
